models

Class GstLabelData

  • java.lang.Object
    • models.GstLabelData

  • public class GstLabelData
extends Object
    POJO to hold data gathered on a label within a generalised suffix tree. Serializable as csv Data on multiple occurences of a label is collected in lists. These lists have to preserve order of insertion such that the client may choose to map information to a specific occurence by identifying the index in that list. TODO: Is LinkedList really more memory efficient for labels than ArrayList?
